				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Thu, 11 Jun 2020 04:18:28 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>fluxman</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>6498353</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I love that this owl is consistent with cream corn. It seems mundane but it twists orders so that it is related to cream corn, but not in a ordinary way. For example it might have given the guy a huge frozen block of cream corn in the shape of a car, but instead fills the car with cream corn.<br /> This was a &quot;slight &quot;hmm&quot; out my nostrils&quot; funny. Interesting article to read.<br /> +1</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
