					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I'm not feeling this in terms of comedy or horror. The &quot;cute stuffed animal turns out to be a terrifying monster&quot; trope has already been done in better ways than this, and this article's insistence on using creamed corn as a prop for a few unfunny bits doesn't change my opinion on this article at all.</p> <p>It's a -1 from me.</p> 
				 	]]>
